replies.body:
What drives you day to day, month to month, season to season to play competitively?

How has competitive league of legends impacted your personality and has that growth really shone into your day to day life?

Ty eGym.{{champion:432}}

I just want to be the best, I think everybody has to have that drive in order to be at least semi successful in the pro(semi-pro?) scene.

I think just competitiveness, I played sports as a kid but I never really cared as much I think.  Competitive league excites me and I want to do everything I can to win for myself and my team.  WILCARDS? WORLDS?!  

ty Raz {{champion:236}}
